l conditioning嚟，到個個都習慣被追蹤，microchip implant就非常易接受 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n加埋用病毒嚇到唔敢用現金，就可以順勢取消現金，全民digital currency，microchip implant連接digital currency account <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.defenseone.com/technology/2020/03/military-funded-biosensor-could-be-future-pandemic-detection/163497/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.defenseone.com%2Ftechnology%2F2020%2F03%2Fmilitary-funded-biosensor-could-be-future-pandemic-detection%2F163497%2F&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=43f7d354\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.defenseone.com/technology/2020/03/military-funded-biosensor-could-be-future-pandemic-detection/163497/</a><br />\n<br />\nmicrochip implant:<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nA Military-Funded Biosensor Could Be the Future of Pandemic Detection<br />\n<br />\nWhy are pandemics so hard to stop? Often it&rsquo;s because the disease moves faster than people can be tested for it. The Defense Department is helping to fund a new study to determine whether an under-the-skin biosensor can help trackers keep up &mdash; by detecting flu-like infections even before their symptoms begin to show. Its maker, Profusa, says the sensor is on track to try for FDA approval by early next year.<br />\n<br />\nThe sensor has two parts. One is a 3mm string of hydrogel, a material whose network of polymer chains is used in some contact lenses and other implants. Inserted under the skin with a syringe, the string includes a specially engineered molecule that sends a fluorescent signal outside of the body when the body begins to fight an infection. The other part is an electronic component attached to the skin. It sends light through the skin, detects the fluorescent signal and generates another signal that the wearer can send to a doctor, website, etc. It&rsquo;s like a blood lab on the skin that can pick up the body&rsquo;s response to illness before the presence of other symptoms, like coughing.<br />\nhydrogel研究都係中國人係MIT帶嘅project <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/ok.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KjpPnOy6cBQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DKjpPnOy6cBQ&d=icC9UeWzMg70WCHWfTItT2WjTds15DFTxBM9bbMqy3g%3D&h=e9b1845c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=KjpPnOy6cBQ</a>"},{"pid":"e643a13f050cf6a69beea00bf929664d2d5a7e0a","tid":2296850,"uid":71428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T02:38:00.000Z","msg":"左膠j 緊強國零確診啦"},{"pid":"6c009fb9e9076641fc23a7c53a49e2ed15413567","tid":2296850,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T23:51:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1e722dbdc351061901437ea7607a681ebf9160d","tid":2296850,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T00:52:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f931afe7f3aa5a1cdebe54a8658df4f9cbb3e5c","tid":2296850,"uid":228894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-26T00:59:49.000Z","msg":"侵侵落選更加唔會成事<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b182a391406ea6cdde9b9d2744631a150e9dfb","tid":2296850,"uid":10998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee6431e1bd74c3dbd4f2d683da653fa92ca8e4db","tid":2296850,"uid":74778,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"quote":{"pid":"6e84d6f71a42ca766977ff52b936259816400c74","tid":2296850,"uid":357936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T01:02:20.000Z","msg":"宜家邊個帶頭追？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-23T03:38:35.000Z","msg":"我都唔明，仲要人帶？